{"tid":2460854,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"大家點樣走出竉物離世嘅陰影","createTime":"2021-03-25T05:46:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T05:58:41.000Z","uid":16123,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ce70f257ccdbd731633e29139aca5e005581cdad","tid":2460854,"uid":16123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T05:46:59.000Z","msg":"由細到大養咗15年嘅狗3-4個月前因為癌症上咗天堂<br />\n到宜家成日諗起佢離開個時個情景就會眼濕濕，返工食食下飯又諗起<br />\n返到屋企係房不時流埋眼淚<br />\n以前都有另一隻狗同樣癌症離開，可能個時有呢隻狗陪先冇咩事<br />\n由細到大冇咩朋友，係得呢隻狗陪我<br />\n宜家走咗，突然覺得人生更加黑暗<br />\n就算想養另一隻，始終都係代替唔到<br />\n想快啲上埋去見佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dafe7feed5115563a9904abc4dd11f5e45e3c38","tid":2460854,"uid":171786,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T05:50:12.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">想快啲上埋去見佢</span><br />\n<br />\n唔好得個想字，即刻做"},{"pid":"c22648f6a99014abb3c1aba327aedaa5c76adbd8","tid":2460854,"uid":270943,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5dafe7feed5115563a9904abc4dd11f5e45e3c38","tid":2460854,"uid":171786,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T05:50:12.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">想快啲上埋去見佢</span><br />\n<br />\n唔好得個想字，即刻做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T05:51:03.000Z","msg":"你覺得自己好幽默？"},{"pid":"bc08f36f44cea71af1b131e80f72046f7f3322ac","tid":2460854,"uid":69168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T05:51:45.000Z","msg":"有個咁愛佢嘅主人佢已經過咗幸福嘅一生，<br />\n我諗佢都希望你可以將呢份愛延續"},{"pid":"d3b55ece5d844c57df4d5b045ba492fbf3284126","tid":2460854,"uid":245409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T05:57:24.000Z","msg":"我都好擔心有呢一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n剩係希望佢到時唔會走得辛苦，痛痛快快咁走<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我一定會喊好耐傷心好耐，我好驚呢一日會黎，但我知終有一日要面對，唯一可以做既就係同佢開心過每一日"},{"pid":"5bbaffcdd665a2d254f14d7cf9a812f0862b98